{"tid":176694,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓皮膚敏感，有冇啲咩藥膏有用？","createTime":"2017-03-28T10:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T15:08:31.000Z","uid":22200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76a1948e69f776f7f7610a46ade14d8ce54fe3a5","tid":176694,"uid":22200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"隻貓之前個鼻同皮膚紅色一忽忽損曬，醫生話佢天生皮膚敏感，又驗過係冇菌。<br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生皮膚好返好多，但係前兩個月左右比左條頸圈佢戴之後，發現佢條頸個圈位冇曬毛，同又係紅曬損曬咁，依家個傷口仲好似嚴重左<br />\n<br />\n想問各位有冇啲咩藥膏可以幫佢搽住先，同埋究竟咩事會搞到咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/183439_ff0d5fb551ab2d7c0c26264aa9092b7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F183439_ff0d5fb551ab2d7c0c26264aa9092b7d.jpg&h=4b159e65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/183453_0783655a999e27996fc210f9140ec466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F183453_0783655a999e27996fc210f9140ec466.jpg&h=637630a5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/183505_6379dd03e5cd2dcd0ec37a1b953cde73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F183505_6379dd03e5cd2dcd0ec37a1b953cde73.jpg&h=28d20435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13b7a7d0b04e48bfa17c6cfc2d6ed6b18b5ccc68","tid":176694,"uid":61359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"爛到咁睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6988924af49c2f641696d2d663ee9d694e93dbb","tid":176694,"uid":22200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"有冇咩藥膏可以買黎搽住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e36a2c44b1276be9c2f182cb79cafce56ab2e2","tid":176694,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"亂咁查藥重衰啦<br />\n而且醫生都話左易敏感重幫佢戴頸圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a10578e7faa171fc69189d350d84be3839f5b4","tid":176694,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔好再戴啦！！快啲睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陰公囉"},{"pid":"fa287ace0f840e57deb496bb8b271357e45cf298","tid":176694,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛到咁睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你快d同貓貓去睇醫生。"}]}